  "title": "Biodiversity Management in Chickpea",
  "abstract": "This chapter focuses on the management of biodiversity in chickpea. The morphological diversity; germplasm collections and enhancement; core and minicore collections and their use for diversity studies and new breeding goals; and the conservation and documentation of chickpea genetic resources are described",
